  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Izmir Hospital PPP</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The EBRD is financing a hospital infrastructure PPP project involving the  design, construction, equipping, financing, and maintenance of an integrated  health campus in Bayrakli, one of the metropolitan districts of Izmir, Turkey,  pursuant to a 28-year concession awarded by Turkey&apos;s Ministry of Health (MoH).  Under this PPP structure, the concessionaire will be responsible for designing,  building, financing, leasing and operating of the hospital facilities, while  the provision of medical care and services will remain the responsibility of  the Ministry of Health.</narrative>
  </description>
